{"id":96,"count":2,"description":"Royal Rajasthan \u2013 Known as the Land of Kings, Rajasthan is a vibrant state that brings history, culture, and royalty to life. With its majestic forts and palaces, colorful bazaars, golden deserts, and rich folk traditions, Rajasthan offers travelers a royal experience like no other. From the shimmering lakes of Udaipur and the pink-hued charm of Jaipur to the golden sands of Jaisalmer, the blue lanes of Jodhpur, and the sacred aura of Pushkar, every corner tells a timeless story of valor and grandeur. Add to this camel safaris, traditional Rajasthani cuisine, and mesmerizing folk music and dance, and Rajasthan becomes a journey into India\u2019s regal past and cultural heart.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/royal-rajasthan\/","name":"ROYAL RAJASTHAN","slug":"royal-rajasthan","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/rajasthan.png","filesize":793659,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"rajasthan-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":71542,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rajasthan-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"rajasthan-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":16037,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rajasthan-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"rajasthan-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":327890,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rajasthan-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"rajasthan-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":95185,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rajasthan-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-size":{"file":"rajasthan-600x596.png","width":600,"height":596,"filesize":314830,"mime_type":"image\/png